name: Oxbull Solana
public_notice: Oxbull Solana (OXS) has migrated to the Polygon network with a new contract and rebranded to Kwai (KWAI). For more information, please view this announcement on Medium. Click here for the new token page.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.
